data.description: Lovely move-in ready two bedroom townhouse in desirable Shadow Brook Estates!! The first floor features an open floor plan with large living room that opens to dining room both with brand new carpeting, a fully-applianced kitchen, half bath (w/linen closet) and access to a new private back deck. The second floor offers a spacious master bedroom with his and her closets and split entry full bath (washer/dryer in bathroom), and large 2nd bedroom with ample sized closet . The unfinished basement is a great space that awaits your personal touches perfect to finish off for additional living space or a dry place for additional storage. The location couldn't be better - you're close to everything (shopping, restaurants, all major traffic routes) yet set away to enjoy the tranquility of life. Call today and schedule your showing!!
